        <h2 class="element-invisible">You are here</h2><ul class="breadcrumbs"><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li class="current"><span>UIC Business Alumni &amp; Community</span></li></ul>
                            <h1 id="page-title" class="title">UIC Business Alumni &amp; Community</h1>
                  
        <a id="main-content"></a>

                                    
        
          
      
      <div  about="/uic-business-alumni-community" typeof="foaf:Document" class="ds-1col node node-page view-mode-full clearfix">

  
  <div class="required-fields group-basic field-group-html-element"><div class="required-fields group-basic-photo field-group-html-element"><div class="field field-name-field-intro-image field-type-image field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://business.uic.edu/sites/default/files/content/fields/intro_image/alumni3.jpg" alt="UIC Business Alumni and Community" title="UIC Business Alumni and Community" /></div></div><div class="required-fields group-basic-text field-group-html-element"><h2 class="field field-name-field-sub-head field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >Welcome</h2><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden field-wrapper body field"><p>A UIC Business degree is more than a credential, it is the background and preparation that gave you the opportunity to have an impact in your profession, community, and beyond. In its half century of existence, our college has grown from three programs to a top-ranked, research-based business school with an international reputation. We have built highly regarded departments in all areas and continue to be recognized by the business community for our outstanding graduates. Our Liautaud Graduate School of Business is nationally recognized and our undergraduate program is ranked the best in Chicago by U.S. News &amp; World Report. Our accreditation by the primary accreditation organization for business schools (AACSB) is something that only 5% of business schools worldwide achieve and we rank among the top 15% of accredited business programs in the country.</p>
<p>We are UIC Business because of you and your support!</p>
<p><a href="http://business.uic.edu/giving"><strong>Make a gift today.</strong></a></p>
</div></div></div>
<div class="paragraphs-items paragraphs-items-field-paragraphs paragraphs-items-field-paragraphs-full paragraphs-items-full">
  <div class="field field-name-field-paragraphs field-type-paragraphs field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><div  about="" typeof="" class="ds-1col entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-image-and-text-1-item view-mode-full clearfix">

  
  <div class="required-fields group-one-item field-group-html-element"><h3 class="field field-name-field-main-title field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >UIC Business Alumni</h3><div class="field field-name-field-main-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><p>As a UIC Business alum, you are one of more than 35,000 men and women who are linked to an influential business network. Even after graduation, our alumni continue to be actively involved with UIC Business and its students – both on and off campus.</p>
<p>UIC Business alumni serve as mentors for current students, as volunteer in Alumni 4 U, and speakers for the <a href="http://blog.business.uic.edu/blog/uicbusiness-stories/executives-in-the-classroom-during-spring-2017">Executives in the Classroom</a> and the <a href="http://business.uic.edu/undergraduate-programs/business-career-center">Business Career Center</a>. They host students at their place of work or take them out to dinner for networking opportunities.</p>
<p>They love UIC Business and the opportunities it presented to them, so they make every effort to keep their Flames spirit alive by giving students access to experiences that enhance their business education. </p>
</div><div class="field field-name-field-main-image field-type-image field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://business.uic.edu/sites/default/files/content/fields/main_image/alumni_network_0.jpg" alt="UIC Business alumni network" title="UIC Business alumni network" /></div></div></div>

<div  about="" typeof="" class="ds-1col entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-text-only-1-item view-mode-full clearfix">

  
  <h3 class="field field-name-field-main-title field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >Are you receiving updates and communication from UIC Business? </h3><div class="required-fields group-item-one field-group-html-element"><div class="field field-name-field-main-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><p>UIC Business is committed to staying connected with our alumni, parents and friends. To ensure you continue to receive news and important information from UIC Business, update your <a href="https://uofi.uic.edu/sb/sec/7033677">contact information online</a>, by phone at (312) 996-5916, or by emailing <a href="mailto:cbalumni@uic.edu">cbalumni@uic.edu</a>.</p>
</div></div></div>

<div  about="" typeof="" class="ds-1col entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-text-only-two-items view-mode-full clearfix">

  
  <div class="required-fields group-item-one field-group-html-element"><div class="group-item-one--wrapper field-group-html-element"><h4 class="field field-name-field-item-1-title field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >Business Advisory Council</h4><div class="field field-name-field-item-1-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><p>UIC Business enjoys support from a Business Advisory Council that works with the dean to provide: ambassadorship and advocacy, pre-professional mentoring of UIC Business undergraduates, and practical business perspectives and advice.  The BAC is composed of leaders from the business world including UIC Business alumni as well as friends who attended other colleges.  For more information, please contact Michaela Smith, Assistant Director of Engagement and Participation at UIC Business, at <a href="mailto:mmsmith1@uic.edu">mmsmith1@uic.edu</a> or (312) 3996-5916.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="required-fields group-item-two field-group-html-element"><div class="group-item-two--wrapper field-group-html-element"><h4 class="field field-name-field-item-2-title field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >Contact Us</h4><div class="field field-name-field-item-2-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><p>Office of Advancement</p>
<p>601 S. Morgan Street<br />UH 2427 (MC 075)<br />Chicago, Illinois 60607<br />Phone: (312) 413-2135<br />Email: <a href="mailto:cbalumni@uic.edu">cbalumni@uic.edu</a></p>
<p>To contribute to UIC Business, please visit the UIC Business <a href="http://business.uic.edu/giving">giving website</a> or contact Courtney Hickman, Associate Director of Donor Relations, (312) 413-3440 or <a href="mailto:hickmanc@uic.edu">hickmanc@uic.edu</a>. Your contributions help make UIC Business more than just a degree; it’s a journey. Thank you for believing in the future of the college and its students. </p>
</div></div></div></div>

</div></div>
</div>

  

